TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {226002=To support this rule, a table is stored in the database that will have a row for each Fiscal Quarter Forecast Period start date for the enterprise. This table will consist of two columns, PERIOD_NAME and START_DATE. The period name will be a string naming the period, ‘FY 2000 Q4’ for example. The start date will be the date of the first day in the period. To determine the fixed baseline forecast date to be used, the closest Fiscal Quarter Period Start that is less than or equal to the current date will be used.}
